original_title: Jack's Mannequin Live from the El Rey Theatre
overview: Jack's Mannequin Live At The El Rey Theatre is a celebration of Jack's Mannequin and the Dear Jack Foundation. Featuring a selection of Andrew McMahon's greatest hits from Something Corporate and Jack's Mannequin, the collection will direct its net profits to the Dear Jack Foundation.
title: Jack's Mannequin Live from the El Rey Theatre
